  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f8270ffd9a996cfa2bca0df66e852826, type: 3}
  m_Name: DemonData_TheBook
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.ScriptableObjects.DemonData_TheBook
  demonName: Ekzeema
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: "Your mind, like paper, tears to shreds.\n\nAnd yet, such a perspective
    you now have, the book, in pieces, matches you.  You are wrapped in its fractured
    words, paper strips entwine you like loving arms. \n\nThe book never needed to
    be fixed, it was you who was broken all along.  The glimmering words sooth your
    ears, seep into the folds of your brain.  From your skull, your eyes look out,
    new eyes look in.\n\nThe moon is a shattered fractal mirror in the sky.\n\nHow
    beautiful."
  minimumPowerLevel: 0
  maximumPowerLevel: 0
  outcome: The game is over, and you found... love? You're alive, at least.
